Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.22,0:00:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH\NDEPARTMENT OF THE ARMY
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.59,0:00:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.30,0:00:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Care for a drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, you're not\Nin the military anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a civilian business owner now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Business is thriving for you, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.77,0:00:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But, what happens if another war\Nbreaks out?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,With the North?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.87,0:00:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Among the Northern Alliance countries\Nled by the Gardarik Empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,there are forces who oppose\Nthe peace agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.21,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you are familiar with\NDrossel's published love letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.47,0:00:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Drossel was one of us, a member\Nof the Southern Union.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Drossel and Fluegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.10,0:01:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A happy marriage between two forces\Nwho were once enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This would be a clear sign\Nto tell the surrounding countries
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that the war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.20,0:01:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,President. I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,THE KINGDOM OF DROSSEL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.46,0:01:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know this is going to be a hard job,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've gained lots of experience\Nin the past few months.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.05,0:01:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So, have confidence in yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.68,0:01:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.89,0:01:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,on writing a good letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.90,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Violet Evergarden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,from CH Postal Company...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.70,0:02:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,is here to request your presence,\NPrincess Charlotte Eberfreya Drossel,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.37,0:02:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I am pleased to make your acquaintance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If it is your wish, I will travel anywhere\Nto meet your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Doll, Violet Evergarden,\Nat your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.56,0:02:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess. I thought I told you\Nabout this meeting the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.77,0:02:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is it the Doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.07,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I am pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Auto Memory Doll, Violet Evergarden,\Nat your service.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.29,0:02:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Charlotte Eberfreya Drossel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm set to marry the prince of Fluegel,\NDamian Baldur Fluegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.30,0:02:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be penning\Nthe published love letter for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.72,0:03:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,your elegant speech is completely ruined\Nwith that appearance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The published love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Its purpose is to express your love\Nfor one another as beautifully as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to convince the people\Nhow wonderful your marriage is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.65,0:03:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It all depends on your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.74,0:03:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am fully aware, Your Highness.\NI will not disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm not talking to a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.50,0:03:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are like a doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.13,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Doll. How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I'm an orphan,\NI do not know my exact age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm told I'm around 14 years of age.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you accept my apology,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.15,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Doll?\N-Please do not worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an issue with my age?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.66,0:04:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just curious\Nabout how others about my age feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.70,0:04:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How much of an age difference\Nis acceptable, do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptable?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The princess is asking whether you'd feel\Ninterested in him romantically.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never experienced romance before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've analyzed statistics\Nbased on literature
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,from many places and eras.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on that knowledge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,there have been many marriages\Nand lovers with large age differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.77,0:04:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,In general, age is not a barrier to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's ten years older?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.48,0:04:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Damian is 24 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it would be an issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if there's no love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.49,0:04:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.83,0:04:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My thoughts on the subject of love are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:05:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Regarding love and loveless marriages,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I lack the information and understanding\Nto provide an answer at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.55,0:05:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What good are you, then?!\NWhat kind of life have you been living?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't even have a decent conversation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm more worried\Nabout your future than mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.06,0:05:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, can't you be more expressive\Nwhen you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, wait a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,"Prince Damian Baldur Fluegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What if I told you that saying your name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.30,0:05:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,or simply writing your name,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.89,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,makes my heart skip?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In this kingdom of flowers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.60,0:05:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,everything makes me think about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and every day, I let out a sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, when I look up at the moon\Nfloating in the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.94,0:06:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,the waning moon looks like\Na flower petal falling to the ground."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE KINGDOM OF FLUEGEL
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"And then I think to myself:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think about\Nwhen you look at the same moon?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.25,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,As instructed, she incorporated\Nthe moon and the flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at writing love letters!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.43,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Impressive. The two countries\Nwill be united soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.35,0:06:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking good so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,"As white as the camellia.\NI praise your beauty,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.07,0:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte Eberfreya Drossel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,-My passionate feelings for you\N-How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,overflow from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:07:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope and desire to have you\Nwith me as soon as possible."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.33,0:07:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It has a beautiful ring to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.31,0:07:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,embarrassed?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.77,0:07:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those weren't tears of embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.19,0:07:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They're tears of frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known the princess\Nsince our queen was pregnant with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess. You know I can find you\Nno matter where you hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.26,0:08:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would hold this against you\Nif I was your mother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You tend to lose control\Nwhen you get emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When you marry into the Fluegel family,\NI, your Alberta, won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the court lady of the royal palace.\NI belong to the royal palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.62,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to you, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.22,0:08:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You snatched me away\Nfrom my mother's womb.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who raised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.39,0:08:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.48,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,who belongs to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough. The letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and you. Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No. I will stay by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.72,0:09:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte.\NHow should we prepare the next letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.49,0:09:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Just write whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.28,0:09:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,His replies are written\Nby a Doll as well, anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Damian is a very busy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.87,0:09:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he's not reading my letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.17,0:09:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,it looks like you're not satisfied\Nwith his replies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:09:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... I've met Damian once before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.06,0:10:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And the Damian I know\Nwouldn't use those kinds of words.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.53,0:10:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I stop being the Princess of Drossel\Nright now, just for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.24,0:10:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit being a Doll right now\Nand listen to my story as your true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Just listen, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The day I turned 10 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a grand banquet was held in Drossel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.31,0:10:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For royal family members,\N10 is already old enough for marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Literally every man I met was a suitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.73,0:10:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't feel like anyone\Nwas celebrating my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't matter how I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.20,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how I was treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. No one's looking for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.90,0:11:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead. It's okay to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.82,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I want to stop crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.86,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw you at the banquet,\NI thought you were such a bratty kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.33,0:11:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to see you cry like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.38,0:11:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the worst birthday party ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I escaped from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand why you would want to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.14,0:12:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.85,0:12:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That man spoke truthfully to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,For me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.49,0:12:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the war intensified\Nand my marriage got put off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But as soon as the war ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I received a marriage offer.\NI was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.59,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this was my only chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I researched and gathered information\Non how our union would benefit both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.18,0:12:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I made an effort to get my father\Nand the Diet to agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.81,0:12:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if that was\Na factor in their decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but Drossel ended up choosing Fluegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.82,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea\Nhow happy I am about this marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.28,0:13:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not sure how he feels about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What if he's actually\Nin love with someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.79,0:13:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're also ten years apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.46,0:13:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not see eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.84,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.97,0:13:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And Alberta won't be there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.43,0:13:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they hate me over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.22,0:13:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything in the letter is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sense his true feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know how he really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know... how he really feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.33,0:14:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.67,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.67,0:14:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We, Auto Memory Dolls,\Nwrite letters for our clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.39,0:14:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot accept requests\Noutside our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be overstepping my bounds\Nwith what I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.89,0:14:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand that my actions\Nare unrelated to CH Postal Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.07,0:14:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stop your tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.83,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,his Doll wrote sound familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,"Princess Charlotte Eberfreya Drossel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,from the garden with the white camellias\Non that moonlit night?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a handwritten letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.73,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rather brief. What is he thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.28,0:15:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a first in history.\NWhat's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:13.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a discussion with his Doll\Nregarding our future exchanges.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.54,0:15:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your turn to write a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Using your own words.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.59,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,"Prince Damian Baldur Fluegel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I do remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.76,0:15:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You laughed at my tear-stained face.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.76,0:15:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was really offended by that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never forgot the sound of your voice\Nwhen you told me it was okay to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I never forgot about your kindness."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,"I laughed because you were cute\Nwhen you acted your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.44,0:15:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't mean to offend you. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my title is 'Prince,'\Nmy personality isn't exactly that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't expect me to be a mature man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We only met that one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of girl are you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How dreamy.\NSounds like a genuine love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm a hot-tempered crybaby.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm probably not the woman\Nof your dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, prince! Comfort the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"I have a little sister, so,\NI'm used to crybabies.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.52,0:16:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not all that great either.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the man of your dreams, either."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, be a man!\NYou're supposed to say, "Come with me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.24,0:16:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's not true since I'm already\Nhead over heels for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Because of the first letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the work of a skilled Doll."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm not in love\Nwith the one in the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm into the person I met 4 years ago\Nwho patted my head under the moonlight."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"I just comforted you that one time\Nbecause you were crying."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've treasured that one moment\Nfor all these years like a precious gem!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'm insensitive and don't understand\Na woman's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I might leave you and go hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably disappoint you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.91,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll meet a better man\Nas you get older."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Excuse me, but what do you mean\Nby a 'better man'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,In terms of their looks? Their wealth?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My idea of a good person\Nis someone who's able to act genuinely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Among everyone I've met,\Nthe only one who admits
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.34,0:17:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,to not being a good man is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I care about.\NThat's all I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.98,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you when you go hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.19,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't underestimate\Nthe Princess of Drossel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm educated so that I'm able\Nto marry into any family!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet I'm a better hunter than you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.87,0:18:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have written that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He must think I'm an ugly brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've had\Nyou write everything, Violet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.92,0:18:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't Alberta stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's his reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.06,0:18:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It says, "I'll be waiting for you\Nin the garden under the moon tonight."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.42,0:18:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Damian?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.46,0:18:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought my reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.59,0:19:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My future bride
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.51,0:19:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to be a smart, strong-willed,\Nand funny person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd make a good queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get married, Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.27,0:19:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Their love has a happy ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.14,0:19:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:19:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Alberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Alberta, I'm over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, you shouldn't tease adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? But I'm a mature adult now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Princess Charlotte,\Nit's time to get dressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.89,0:20:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Alberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think Violet is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have left the country by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You look beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish Violet could've seen me\Nin my wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are your worries gone now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.46,0:20:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gone? Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the verge of crying right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You must not cry.\NYou're about to set off on a new journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my dream to marry Prince Damian.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.60,0:21:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But I hate that I have to leave my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.98,0:21:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But what I really dread\Nis to be separated from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,more than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Alberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.67,0:21:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.96,0:21:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alberta.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Violet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.62,0:22:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.58,0:22:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was hard to convince\NPrince Damian to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.09,0:22:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to eat steak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.13,0:22:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I owe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.39,0:22:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.31,0:22:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.82,0:22:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Today is such a beautiful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.90,0:22:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.74,0:22:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.58,0:22:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A beautiful day for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,LEIDENSCHAFTLICH\NPORT OF LEIDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.42,0:23:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.76,0:23:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Diethard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.22,0:23:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Navy Captain Bougainvillea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.64,0:23:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard rumors about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.85,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you really did become\Nan Auto Memory Doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.98,0:23:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who killed so many of my comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.37,0:23:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Writing letters...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.29,0:23:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with the very hand\Nthat took the lives of so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.26,0:23:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You write letters\Nthat bring people together?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.97,0:23:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Subtitle translation by\NSachiko Takahashi
